Putting it all together: the creation of a new domain user, adding them to Domain Admins, using suspicious executables (net1.exe), and possible configuration changes. These activities are indicative of an attacker trying to escalate privileges or set up persistence. Therefore, this batch is interesting and requires further investigation.
